T*
(interesting in biology. Lacking an academic peer group, I?m using a series of blog posts to) Tj
T*
(gather feedback and to keep myself honest. Because chances continue to be high that as an) Tj
T*
(outsider I am deluding myself. The full backstory can be found in part 1 without which this) Tj
T*
(installment will not make much sense.) Tj
